      <h1 class="display-1">Mortgage Marketing Careers: The Creative Path</h1>
      <p class="lead hero-subtitle">Love creating content, designing, writing, or making videos &mdash; but don't want to make sales calls? The marketing path is your way into the mortgage industry. Build the brand and generate the leads that power the whole business, playing to your creative strengths.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://forms.stairwaymortgage.com/widget/survey/WGombd892PhSYF3yMwH9?slug=branches-careers-internships" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Start My Mortgage Career</a>
